    "updated_at": "2015-07-17T13:02:20Z",
    "body": "Regarding @zcbenz \"I think it actually matches the style of other modern Windows apps?\", Microsoft encourages the behavior; on [MSDN > Dialog boxes](https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/windows/desktop/dn742499%28v=vs.85%29.aspx):\n\n> - **Always provide an explicit Cancel button.** Don't use a command link for this purpose.\n\nMy vote would go to complete control. The documentation should also probably link to the aforementioned MSDN design guidelines.\n"
  },
